snippet.title: ANTRO 🎵🎮 | Gameplay Teaser - DEMO AVAILABLE NOW!
snippet.description:
#videogame #indiegame #rhythmgame 
🎮DEMO NOW AVAILABLE ON STEAM! Try it and wishlist it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1861250/Antro/

It's the underground revolution. Join Nittch and the Discordants in the race to overthrow La Cúpula. In this rhythm, action, puzzle and 2.5D platforming game, music will be your ally!

Journey through the most remote places in the underground metropolis of ANTRO. Your mission is to deliver a package with an unknown recipient and, while you’re at it, overthrow the totalitarian government of La Cúpula. 

Available in 2024.
